main event: Observers at Galena AFS, Alaska, reported seeing two unidentified objects in the sky, one stationary and the other moving, with the observation lasting between 30 seconds to 15 minutes.
interesting points: The objects were described as spherical in shape, with colors changing from red to green to white.,Personnel on duty noted changes in color and intensity of the moving object.,A search was conducted by two F-106 jets for 70 minutes with no results.,The moving light was possibly identified as a satellite.,Witnesses provided conflicting testimonies about the speed and distance of the objects.
sighted object: two spherical objects in the sky
witness description: Military personnel stationed at Galena AFS.
